{"tid":2407620,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"情人節│楊潤雄引孟子談情「說愛」　讓家庭學校社會充滿愛與關懷","createTime":"2021-02-14T07:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T08:16:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1bc08f4ce8f90a508f6c26d55f6e3b6442d05732","tid":2407620,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T07:42:32.000Z","msg":"今天(14日)是情人節，教育局局長楊潤雄在社交網站特別貼文，祝大家情人節快樂，又引用中華經典名句--儒家代表孟子來談情「說愛」，可以由自己做起，讓家庭、學校和社會充滿愛與關懷。<br />\n<br />\n孟子説：「愛人者，人恆愛之。」<br />\n<br />\n根據教育局向中小學提供的中華經典名句解說：<br />\n孟子認為品德高尚的人，心中經常保存「仁」和「禮」。由於內心存「仁」，所以能夠愛他人；由於內心存「禮」，所以能尊敬別人。當一個人以怎樣的方式對待別人，別人便會以同樣的方式回報他。你能愛人，別人也會愛你；你能敬人，別人也會敬你。在家庭中，一家人的相處，相愛相敬，應該容易做到，但在學校裏，接觸的人多了，溝通的技巧更須注意。孟子的話，很值得我們反覆細味。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2875000/2877743/yeung01_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2875000%2F2877743%2Fyeung01_1024.JPG&h=33901d0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45bb7779f3a08628b98e3fafb666db12b1c43d91","tid":2407620,"uid":42982,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T07:48:01.000Z","msg":"聞誅一夫紂矣，未嘗弒君也。<br />\n<br />\n孟子亦支持以武抗暴"},{"pid":"183c40b1fa3062d1330a3405acdd58a0c9dbe6e3","tid":2407620,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T07:50:59.000Z","msg":"你商科佬嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d85b1370579be55e4fa8581b5d2f3354593e26","tid":2407620,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45bb7779f3a08628b98e3fafb666db12b1c43d91","tid":2407620,"uid":42982,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T07:48:01.000Z","msg":"聞誅一夫紂矣，未嘗弒君也。<br />\n<br />\n孟子亦支持以武抗暴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53942fa47378319096ffd715e52f096d01a76ecd","tid":2407620,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T07:52:51.000Z","msg":"殺人者，人恆誅之。"},{"pid":"84e37b510f930e2c8e523d42e973cbba8a8a03f6","tid":2407620,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T07:53:23.000Z","msg":"楊狗收皮啦"},{"pid":"02829add624d6bc5954b1790f88e628beff502a9","tid":2407620,"uid":7363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:13:17.000Z","msg":"批鬥教師佢就叻，仲話愛人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e891f4a7c705ed3093e6ef5e4ae4c32f4fbed7e3","tid":2407620,"uid":205594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:16:52.000Z","msg":"孟子話民貴君輕，收皮啦會計佬。"}]}